 5. The rewards system is trash, those CP, AP, or other Ps are just the number, I worked my ass off to get enough CP and went to buy the item ended up with nearly nothing changed of my status and still get kicked in my ass. STILL, bad experience. -20 (btw, it is not because I don't like to spend time on games, I do, but the point is I can't get satisfied after I get the item, work and gain ain't equal)
